{"tid":1269733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港獨立黨將發起公投 Media invitation: Important Announcement","createTime":"2019-06-30T16:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T11:57:58.000Z","uid":92301,"like":115,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c3494f5b732bc10947870f08c41a9128a594c6aa","tid":1269733,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:03:20.000Z","msg":"With regard to the recent social instability, Hong Kong Independence Party (HKIP) is going to announce its plans and actions for the failure of Sino-British Joint Declaration; the rights of British National (Overseas) holders; and Hong Kong independence. You and your representatives are cordially invited to attend the press event. Details are as follow:<br />\nDate: 1 July 2019<br />\nTime:&nbsp;11am<br />\nVenue: In front of the British Consulate General Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nHKIP will also be holding a referendum for the citizens of Hong Kong to decide the future of this City:<br />\n(1) be part of the United Kingdom;<br />\n(2) be independent; or&nbsp;<br />\n(3) remains everything unchanged under the Basic Law<br />\n<br />\nFor enquiries, please contact Mr. KC Wong via hongkongindependenceparty@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\nKind regards,&nbsp;<br />\nKC Wong&nbsp;FRSA, FCollT, FLCM, FTCL&nbsp;Chairman United Kingdom<br />\nAlexander Robinson Trustee Japan"},{"pid":"04998486943b55c77b85539adf0b3ea34223b6fd","tid":1269733,"uid":177168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:06:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f31fd6581738d30780694fad3b56006a9846de2","tid":1269733,"uid":262072,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:08:14.000Z","msg":"路祥安"},{"pid":"42102f3c484d5f21531ff352b62b61c333ff049b","tid":1269733,"uid":169074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:10:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"216210e2df93c35a050316ac3e0adec9bb3f2fe1","tid":1269733,"uid":107572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:26:15.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5280c809f979b01d4faac7563ecc8355bbec420f","tid":1269733,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:41:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c4c34d20caa50de3a8ad5ca2b08345c14e4ae6","tid":1269733,"uid":5662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:43:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"651148020a171d9d06b43595c0729459ca2251c1","tid":1269733,"uid":92301,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:43:11.000Z","msg":"回應香港近來社會紛爭，香港獨立黨（HKIP）將會舉辦一「香港自決前途公投」<br />\n<br />\n目的：為香港市民於公投對香港前途表態<br />\n對象：全香港市民<br />\n<br />\n公投選項如下：<br />\n1. 加入聯合王國（英國）<br />\n2. 香港獨立<br />\n3. 維持現狀（中國特別行政區）"},{"pid":"ac3eea523907b37044eb5da28aa973798790f6a1","tid":1269733,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士表示關注"},{"pid":"f110138328dcb1fe58f2a9113884c8b55687a0a9","tid":1269733,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:44:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbf06fc58f02bb3d69c8379ab093c4f01dd510f2","tid":1269733,"uid":229777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:45:45.000Z","msg":"push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07f4670b51a5260540495e7c512aa29da6b2cf9","tid":1269733,"uid":99582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:47:11.000Z","msg":"我就一定支持(2) 但投完有無後續!?"},{"pid":"4008e1896cb7a9178885c3b9925feef52f6aa56e","tid":1269733,"uid":3571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:47:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"237ac3f2b1960f2410fdef195163bd3300f59684","tid":1269733,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:49:00.000Z","msg":"冇BNO咪冚家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s